stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> closed : 会话开始，failures=0
    closed --> closed : 压缩成功\nfailures=0（重置）
    closed --> half_open : 压缩失败\nfailures=1
    half_open --> half_open : 压缩失败\nfailures=2
    half_open --> open_state : failures >= 3\n熔断
    open_state --> open_state : 平能尝试均跳过
    closed --> closed : wasCompacted=true\nfailures重置=0
    Note: 新会话即重置，不需要定时实探
